{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "syspro-enet-collection",
    "name": "SYSPRO e.net API Collection",
    "description": "Complete collection for testing SYSPRO e.net Solutions API.\n\n**Setup:**\n1. Set variables in Environment\n2. Run \"Login\" first to get SessionId\n3. SessionId auto-saves to environment\n4. Always run \"Logout\" when done\n\n**Environment Variables Needed:**\n- `baseUrl`: SYSPRO e.net URL (e.g., http://server:30000)\n- `operator`: SYSPRO operator username\n- `password`: Operator password\n- `companyId`: Company code (A, B, T, etc.)\n- `sessionId`: Auto-populated after login",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://syspro-server:30000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "operator",
      "value": "ADMIN",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "password",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "companyId",
      "value": "A",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "sessionId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Authentication",
      "description": "Login and logout operations",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "// Parse response",
                  "var responseText = pm.response.text();",
                  "",
                  "// Check for error",
                  "if (responseText.includes('<ErrorMessage>')) {",
                  "    var errorMatch = responseText.match(/<ErrorMessage>([^<]+)<\\/ErrorMessage>/);",
                  "    var error = errorMatch ? errorMatch[1] : 'Unknown error';",
                  "    pm.test('Login should succeed', function() {",
                  "        pm.expect.fail('Login failed: ' + error);",
                  "    });",
                  "} else {",
                  "    // Extract SessionId - it's returned as plain text GUID",
                  "    var sessionId = responseText.trim();",
                  "    ",
                  "    // Basic GUID validation",
                  "    var guidRegex = /^[0-9a-f]{8}-[0-9a-f]{4}-[0-9a-f]{4}-[0-9a-f]{4}-[0-9a-f]{12}$/i;",
                  "    ",
                  "    if (guidRegex.test(sessionId)) {",
                  "        // Save to collection variable",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('sessionId', sessionId);",
                  "        ",
                  "        pm.test('Login successful', function() {",
                  "            pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "        });",
                  "        ",
                  "        console.log('SessionId saved: ' + sessionId);",
                  "    } else {",
                  "        pm.test('Valid SessionId received', function() {",
                  "            pm.expect.fail('Invalid SessionId format: ' + sessionId);",
                  "        });",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/xml"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "<Logon>\n  <Operator>{{operator}}</Operator>\n  <OperatorPassword>{{password}}</OperatorPassword>\n  <CompanyId>{{companyId}}</CompanyId>\n  <CompanyPassword></CompanyPassword>\n</Logon>"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/saborw/Logon",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["saborw", "Logon"]
            },
            "description": "**Login to SYSPRO e.net**\n\nReturns a SessionId (GUID) that must be used for all subsequent API calls.\n\n**Important:**\n- SessionId is automatically saved to collection variables\n- Session counts against license until logout or 20-minute timeout\n- Always logout when done!"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Logout successful', function() {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "// Clear session",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('sessionId', '');",
                  "console.log('SessionId cleared');"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/xml"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{{sessionId}}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/saborw/Logoff",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["saborw", "Logoff"]
            },
            "description": "**Logout from SYSPRO**\n\nReleases the session and frees the license.\n\n**Always run this when done testing!**"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Inventory",
